              "role": "PROMPT",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "Combine each pair of sentences with the connectors given in brackets. Make any necessary changes.\na. Bullied students feel very depressed. Bullied students end up dropping out of school. (so...that)\nb. Bullying is physical violence. Bullying is verbal violence. (both...and)"
